{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "The second phase carried out the annotation for the, unlabeled tweets.",
    "The system used extraction features, such as TF, TF-IDF (n-gram, character level), and word embedding with 13 machine learning algorithms, including KNN, DT, LR, MNB, Linear Support Vector Machines (LSVM), BNB, Perceptron, NN, XGB, Ensemble Random Forest (ERF), Bagging Meta-Estimator (BME), Gradient Boosting (GB), and AdaBoost.",
    "Meanwhile, Haouari et al. [75] built the ArCOV19-Rumors dataset, which covered some claims about COVID-19.",
    "The research presented a benchmark on claim-level verification and tweetlevel verification to exploit the content, user profiles, propagation structure, and temporal features.",
    "The Bidirectional Graph CN (Bi-GCN) and RNN+CNN, as well as the AraBERT and MARBERT models were tested on the dataset."
  ],
